After using this app you will be able to understand parts of a sentence. These are nouns, pronouns, verbs, helping verbs,
articles, adjectives, adverbs, conjunctions, prepositions, objective pronouns, possessive pronouns, and possessive adjectives.

Who can use this app: This app is helpful for those who do not know English or know little and want to improve their English grammar knowledge.
It also helps students of schools, colleges, and English language proficiency exams, like PTE, TOEFL, and IELTS.
As it provides step by step easy guide to make sentence according to grammar rules.

How this app works: In this app, we can do sentence making exercises. This app uses artificial intelligence to makes a sentence
according to grammar rules. When a person tries to make a sentence use these rules again and again he learns by repetition. It helps to understand the structure of a sentence, recognize and remember part of the sentence. which are also parts of speech so it also helps to speak English.
you can also learn how to make a combination of words in sentences according to grammar rules.

This app has a list of verbs. It shows the first form of the verb, second form of the verb, and the third form of the verb, also use of 'ing' and 's' / 'es' and guides us to use the verb in the sentence. Step by step we learn tenses and the use of verbs and helping verbs(axillary verbs) in tenses. Exercise also enables students to differentiate between subjects and objects. 
  
App has easy navigation just follow the arrow after click the start button. On the next page choose tense -> then choose Pronoun -> choose verb\helping verb ( you can choose a verb from the verb list
or search verb in the search box)-> choose object -> on the last page, then you will see words used in the sentence and their name in grammar. 

Apart from this app also have a brief description of topics Like tenses, sentence, verb, object, predicate, etc. Just click the link given at the home page and read about these topics.  
